item.title: Nullbyte 1 solution
item.description: I’ve been AFK for a while because of various reasons, but now I’m back and have managed to scrape a little time together to get on with some of Vulnhub’s new VMs. So let’s start with Nullbyte 1 Stage 1 I ran the usual service discovery and found: root@kali:~# nmap -sV 192.168.56.101 Starting Nmap 6.49BETA4 ( https://nmap.org ) at 2015-08-25 11:29 BST Nmap scan report for 192.168.56.101 Host is up (0.00057s latency).
